<div class="dashboard" style="padding-top: 120px;">
    <div class="card" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 32px; text-align: center;">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        
        <div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-purple); margin-bottom: 12px;">What is Maximum?</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
                Maximum is a professional cryptocurrency trading platform that allows you to trade Bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies safely and successfully with real-time price tracking.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-purple); margin-bottom: 12px;">How do I start trading?</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
                Simply create an account, verify your email, and deposit funds to start trading. Our platform provides expert guidance for both beginners and experienced traders.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-purple); margin-bottom: 12px;">Is my money safe?</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
                Yes, we use industry-standard security measures including encryption, secure authentication, and regular security audits to protect your funds and data.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-purple); margin-bottom: 12px;">What cryptocurrencies can I trade?</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
                Currently we support Bitcoin (BTC) with plans to add Ethereum (ETH), Litecoin (LTC), and other major cryptocurrencies soon.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-purple); margin-bottom: 12px;">How do I contact support?</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
                You can reach our support team 24/7 through the contact form on our website or email us at support@maximum.com
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

